{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before we got-- went through the gates, he said, this, this is-- this is going to blow you away or something to that effect.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, and there was a train that was probably 60, 80 cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it had been-- it was on a side track, and it was-- he drove us down the railroad track, me and another guy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was, you know, kind of like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he said, look in those cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was filled with dead-- with dead people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean every car.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Most of them were naked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some of them had been shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were medics, guys that had the Red Cross on their helmets and on their shoulders, going through these bodies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I guess they found a few, I don't know, alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were bodies alongside the track, which had been shot, men had-- men who had been shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You could see the blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then there were also bodies along there that there were no blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we spent about 30 minutes going up one side, and I got out and looked in some of the cars.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, and I'd had no idea what the hell was going on, except this train was full of dead people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then he said, I'll show you where the firefight was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So he went to back toward the gate, and we went through the gate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now there was guards on the gate who were ordered not to let anybody in or anybody out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When we got to the gate, I told the guard I was with [INAUDIBLE] and I had a [INAUDIBLE] pass.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he said, well, I'm sorry, sir.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Nobody in, nobody out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
